data.description: NO HOA!!! Amazing potential for this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with a pool on this awesome over-sized lot!!! Home appraised for 425k in Jan 2023. Close to the Airport, The Strip, plenty of great restaurants and shopping. Kitchen features granite counter tops, tinted windows, vaulted ceiling and ceramic tile flooring! Front door opens up to the living room with a fireplace and vaulted ceilings! 4th bedroom can be used as a Den/Office and is right off the living room. Spacious backyard for your perfect oasis in the city. SOLAR SYSTEM helps you save money against those rising energy bills!
